            <div class="clearfix post-meta post-meta-bottom"> <span class="rtp-meta-cat">Categories: </span> <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/category/news-items/" title="View all posts in News Items" rel="tag">News Items</a>        <span class="rtp-post-comment-count"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/02/14/subprime-mortgages-are-back-this-time-marketed-as-second-chance-purchase-programs/#comments" class="rtp-post-comment rtp-common-link"  title="Comment on Subprime Mortgages are Back&#8230;This Time Marketed as &#8220;Second Chance Purchase Programs&#8221;"><span>3</span> Comments</a></span><span class="post-tags"> Tags:  <span><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/blackstone/" rel="tag">Blackstone</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/citadel-servicing-corp/" rel="tag">Citadel Servicing Corp</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/fha/" rel="tag">FHA</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/housing-bubble/" rel="tag">Housing Bubble</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/invitation-homes/" rel="tag">Invitation Homes</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/wells-fargo/" rel="tag">Wells Fargo</a></span></span>                <span class="post-tags">Comments: </span><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/02/14/subprime-mortgages-are-back-this-time-marketed-as-second-chance-purchase-programs/#comments">5</a> 
            </div><!-- .post-meta --></footer>
            
